Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:44.56,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}究竟人類 為何而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:48.23,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}哪怕生命 流逝消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:52.14,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}這無盡的煩惱
